summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 and 2, Block 1; Lots 1 and 2, Block 2, Drexel Heights Addition; et al, located on 34th Avenue between East Columbia Street and East Spring Street; Lots 14 and 15, Block 21, of the proposed City Plat of the Sears Tract; located on the west side of Rainier Avenue, between Holden Street, and Austin Street, et al; and amending Ordinance 45382, as amended.
